<h2>About the Project</h2>
<p>
  This capstone project is an intelligent, AI-powered forecasting and decision-support system designed to assist Local Government Units (LGUs), farmers, and agricultural officers in improving agricultural planning, productivity, and sustainability. The system integrates artificial intelligence, predictive analytics, and real-time weather data to provide accurate forecasts and actionable insights that support data-driven decision-making in the agricultural sector.
</p>